|=============================================================================================================================|
|                                                   GENERAL DESCRIPTIONS                                                      |
|=============================================================================================================================|
|       In this chapter, you will learn how to apply different geometric transformations to images, such as                   |                                                                                   |
|                   1) Translation.                                                                                           |
|                   2) Rotation.                                                                                              |
|                   3) Affine transformation.                                                                                 |
|                   4) Perpective transformation & Resize an image.                                                           |
|                   5) Some arthimetic operations between more than 2 images.                                                 |
|                   6) Blending & Overlapping multi-images.                                                                   |
|=============================================================================================================================|
